#: ../../../gpu-programming/execution-model.md:1
msgid "The CUDA Execution Model"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../gpu-programming/execution-model.md:3
msgid ""
"This chapter covers the CUDA SIMT execution model -- how work is organized "
"into threads, warps, blocks, and grids -- and how cuda-oxide exposes each "
"level through safe, ergonomic Rust APIs."
msgstr ""

